<p>Image sources: <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:1st_Home,_The_NY_Foundling_Hospital_-_17_E_12th_St_-_circa_1900_-_Byron_Company_-_MNY10815.jpg">1</a>, <a href="http://www.gutenberg.org/files/28024/28024-h/28024-h.html">2</a>, <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Patients_and_staff_at_Croydon_District_Hospital_ca._1920.tif">3</a>. All are in the public domain in the USA due to copyright expiration (pre-1923).</p>

